comments: Green (WAS) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Fox (SAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Green (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Bjelica (SAC) moves laterally into Beal's (WAS) path at the start of his drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Satoransky's (WAS) path and gives him room to avoid contact.
Portis (WAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Fox (SAC).
Hield (SAC) makes contact to Portis' (WAS) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Satoransky's (WAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Green (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and briefly grasps and releases Hield's arm but the contact does not affect his FOM.
Cauley-Stein (SAC) collapses his arm and absorbs the contact from Beal (WAS) when he contests the driving shot attempt.
Satoransky (WAS) makes contact to Fox's (SAC) body during his shooting motion that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) grabs and holds Green's (WAS) arm and the contact affects his FOM.
Green (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Portis (WAS) maintains legal guarding position when contesting Hield's (SAC) shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Beal (WAS) briefly engage and separate while rebounding.
Barnes (SAC) commits a take foul on Satoransky (WAS).
Green (WAS) maintains legal guarding position when he contests Hield's (SAC) shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact to Portis's (WAS) right arm prior to cleanly dislodging the ball.
Portis (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Barnes (SAC) during his shooting motion that does not affect his shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) body and affects his ability to secure the rebound.
